nction"><strong style="color:#CC7832">gzclose()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"><div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$gz </span><span style="color: #007700">= </span><span style="color: #9876AA">gzopen</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'somefile.gz'</span><span style="color: #007700">,</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'w9'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">gzputs </span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$gz</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'I was added to somefile.gz'</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">gzclose</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$gz</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span></span></span></div>    </div>   </div>  </span> </div> <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.gzclose-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <span>   <ul class="simplelist">    <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link gzopen()} - Open gz-file</span></li>   </ul>  </span> </div></div>
